# Tech Stack

> Version: 1.0.0
> Last Updated: 2025-01-27
> Based on: LiveThrough Project Analysis

## Context

This file is part of the Agent OS standards system. These global tech stack defaults are referenced by all product codebases when initializing new projects. Individual projects may override these choices in their `.agent-os/product/tech-stack.md` file.

## Core Technologies

### Application Framework
- **Framework:** Next.js
- **Version:** 15.2.4+
- **Language:** TypeScript 5.0+
- **Architecture:** App Router with Server Components

### Database & Backend
- **Backend-as-a-Service:** Supabase
- **Database:** PostgreSQL (managed by Supabase)
- **Authentication:** Supabase Auth + NextAuth.js
- **Real-time:** Supabase subscriptions

## Frontend Stack

### JavaScript Framework
- **Framework:** React
- **Version:** 19.0.0+
- **Build Tool:** Next.js (Turbopack)
- **Package Manager:** npm

### TypeScript Configuration
- **Target:** ES2017
- **Module Resolution:** bundler
- **Strict Mode:** Enabled
- **Path Aliases:** `@/*` for root imports

### CSS Framework
- **Framework:** TailwindCSS
- **Version:** 4.0+
- **PostCSS:** Yes (with @tailwindcss/postcss)
- **CSS Variables:** Enabled
- **Base Color:** Black theme

### UI Components
- **Library:** Radix UI primitives
- **Component System:** shadcn/ui (New York style)
- **Icons:** Lucide React
- **Animations:** Framer Motion

## Key Libraries

### Rich Text Editing
- **Editor:** TipTap
- **Version:** 3.0.0-beta.17
- **Extensions:** Starter kit + custom extensions (highlight, image, link, etc.)

### Data Visualization
- **Charts:** Recharts
- **Version:** 2.15.3+

### Utilities
- **Date Handling:** date-fns
- **Class Utilities:** clsx + class-variance-authority
- **Toast Notifications:** Sonner
- **Image Processing:** Sharp (server-side)

## Infrastructure

### Application Hosting
- **Platform:** Vercel (recommended for Next.js)
- **Alternative:** Netlify, Railway, or self-hosted

### Database Hosting
- **Provider:** Supabase
- **Service:** Managed PostgreSQL
- **Backups:** Automated daily backups
- **Real-time:** Built-in subscriptions

### Asset Storage
- **Provider:** Supabase Storage
- **Image Processing:** Sharp for WebP conversion
- **CDN:** Supabase CDN

## Development Tools

### Code Quality
- **Linting:** ESLint with Next.js config
- **Type Checking:** TypeScript strict mode
- **Formatting:** Prettier (recommended)

### Development Environment
- **Node Version:** 18+ (LTS recommended)
- **Package Manager:** npm
- **Environment Variables:** .env.local for local development

## Deployment

### CI/CD Pipeline
- **Platform:** Vercel (recommended)
- **Alternative:** GitHub Actions
- **Trigger:** Push to main branch
- **Preview:** Automatic PR deployments

### Environments
- **Production:** main branch
- **Preview:** PR-based deployments
- **Development:** local development

### Build Configuration
- **Image Optimization:** Next.js built-in
- **Server Actions:** Enabled with 10MB body limit
- **External Packages:** Sharp for image processing

## Authentication & Security

### Authentication Strategy
- **Primary:** Supabase Auth
- **Secondary:** NextAuth.js for additional features
- **Session Management:** Supabase SSR helpers

### Security Features
- **CORS:** Configured for specific domains
- **Image Upload:** Chunked upload with validation
- **API Routes:** Server-side validation

